                  backgrounds (e.g. images).</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><p>y_waste</p></td>  <td><p>Amount of vertical waste (over-print) to allow.  This is useful
                  for minimizing alignment problems when using non-white
                  backgrounds (e.g. images).</p></td>
